snippet.textDisplay: I dont know why but this piece evokes so much emotions, The Hymn in the beginning gradually gives the song a fade in, then the chorus gives the calmness and a lullaby type of feel, then the Solo percussion and the scale of the melody gives me a darker feel then the groove and Farah Siraj's vocals gives a different unusual feeling. All these are life's different phases in itself. Thank you Rahman sir and other musicians for this beautiful piece ♥️
